<div class="container site-section main-section">
    <h1 class="text-center">Collector Services</h1>
    <p style="font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:18px; color:#444; max-width:750px; margin:0 auto 50px auto; text-align:center; line-height:1.7;">Tony offers a select range of professional services for serious collectors and long-time clients. These services are available by application only — please review each program below and reach out if you'd like to apply.</p>

    <!-- Service 1: Auction Representation -->
    <div style="background:white; border:1px solid #e0e5ea; border-radius:20px; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:50px; box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);">
        <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <!-- Image -->
            <div style="flex:0 0 380px; max-width:380px; min-height:300px; background-image:url('/assets/img/IMG_5804.JPG'); background-size:cover; background-position:40% 50%;">
            </div>
            <!-- Content -->
            <div style="flex:1; min-width:280px; padding:40px;">
                <div style="display:inline-block; background:#e8f0fb; color:#1d3961; font-family:'Roboto'; font-weight:700; font-size:12px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:20px; margin-bottom:16px;">By Application Only</div>
                <h2 style="font-family:'Noto Serif Display'; font-weight:800; color:#1d3961; font-size:28px; margin-bottom:16px;">Auction Representation</h2>
                <p style="font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:16px; color:#444; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:20px;">When significant money is on the line, online photography simply isn't enough. Tony attends major auction lot viewings in person and delivers professional, in-hand assessments — helping you decide whether to pass or bid with confidence.</p>

                <!-- Tier 1 -->
                <div style="background:#f3f6f9; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; margin-bottom:16px; border-left:4px solid #6289c1;">
                    <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px;">
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="font-family:'Noto Serif Display'; font-weight:800; color:#1d3961; font-size:18px; margin:0 0 6px 0;">Lot Viewing & Opinion Report</h3>
                            <p style="font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:15px; color:#555; margin:0; line-height:1.6;">In-person lot inspection with a written professional opinion on each piece — condition, eye appeal, value assessment, and a clear pass/bid recommendation.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div style="text-align:center; width:100%;">
                            <div style="font-family:'Noto Serif Display'; font-weight:800; color:#1d3961; font-size:22px;">$150<span style="font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#888;">/hr</span></div>
                            <div style="font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:12px; color:#888; margin-top:2px;">2-hour minimum</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Tier 2 -->
                <div style="background:#f3f6f9; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; border-left:4px solid #1d3961;">
                    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:8px;">
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="font-family:'Noto Serif Display'; font-weight:800; color:#1d3961; font-size:18px; margin:0 0 6px 0;">Full-Service Bid & Delivery</h3>
                            <p style="font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:15px; color:#555; margin:0 0 8px 0; line-height:1.6;">Complete white-glove service including lot viewing, 1-1 consultation, live bid execution in Cabbage Coins' name, delivery acceptance from the auction house, and insured shipping to you.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div style="text-align:center; width:100%;">
                            <span style="font-family:'Noto Serif Display'; font-weight:800; color:#1d3961; font-size:22px;">5%</span>
                            <span style="font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:15px; color:#555; margin-left:4px;">of hammer price ($750 minimum)</span>
                        </div>
                        <p style="font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:12px; color:#888; margin:0;">If the lot is not won, a 1% fee of the winning hammer price applies.</p>

                        </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 2: Consignment Program -->
    <div style="background:white; border:1px solid #e0e5ea; border-radius:20px; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:50px; box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);">
        <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; flex-direction:row-reverse;">
            <!-- Image -->
            <div style="flex:0 0 380px; max-width:380px; min-height:300px; background-image:url('/assets/img/IMG_7516.JPEG'); background-size:cover; background-position:center;">
            </div>
            <!-- Content -->
            <div style="flex:1; min-width:280px; padding:40px;">
                <div style="display:inline-block; background:#e8f0fb; color:#1d3961; font-family:'Roboto'; font-weight:700; font-size:12px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:20px; margin-bottom:16px;">By Application Only</div>
                <h2 style="font-family:'Noto Serif Display'; font-weight:800; color:#1d3961; font-size:28px; margin-bottom:16px;">Consignment Program</h2>
                <p style="font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:16px; color:#444; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:20px;">For collectors who want professional representation of their coins across multiple markets. Cabbage Coins handles the full sales process — from photography to show floor presence — while you retain ownership until the sale is complete.</p>

                <div style="background:#f3f6f9; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; margin-bottom:16px; border-left:4px solid #6289c1;">
                    <h3 style="font-family:'Noto Serif Display'; font-weight:800; color:#1d3961; font-size:18px; margin:0 0 12px 0;">What's Included</h3>
                    <ul style="font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:15px; color:#555; line-height:1.8; padding-left:20px; margin:0;text-align:left;">
                        <li>Professional photography of each coin</li>
                        <li>Publication on the Cabbage Coins website</li>
                        <li>Display and active selling at regional and national coin shows</li>
                        <li>Option for a dedicated collection webpage <em>(e.g. "The XYZ Mercury Dime Collection")</em> or integration into the existing inventory</li>
                        <li>Agreed-upon pricing in writing before any publication or display</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div style="background:#f3f6f9; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; border-left:4px solid #1d3961; text-align:center;">
                    <h3 style="font-family:'Noto Serif Display'; font-weight:800; color:#1d3961; font-size:18px; margin:0 0 4px 0;">Commission Rate</h3>
                    <p style="font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:14px; color:#888; margin:0 0 12px 0;">No upfront fees. Commission is only charged upon sale.</p>
                    <div style="font-family:'Noto Serif Display'; font-weight:800; color:#1d3961; font-size:22px;">10% <span style="font-size:15px; font-weight:400; color:#555;">of final sale price</span></div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

